Commons Economy Roadmap:

"The emerging international network of communities, small to medium internet service providers (ISPs) and blockchain-based protocols like Althea Network, with the goal of decentralizing the provision of internet services. This multitude is moved by a mix of traditional economic incentives, needs to be addressed and ethical values."


